Package com.intel.icecp.core.permissions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasePermission
    Implement basic name and action matching for extension by descendant classes.
    ChannelPermission
    Controls use of a Channel; allowed actions are: [close, open, publish, subscribe].
    ChannelProviderPermission
    Controls use of a ChannelProvider; allowed actions are: [register, shutdown, unregister], defined in ChannelProviderPermission.Action.
    KeyManagementPermissions
    Permissions regulating access to keys and certificates
    ModulePermission
    Controls use of a Module; allowed actions are: [start, access, stop].
    NodePermission
    Control access to the device; each permission will have an action in [network, read, write].
    Tpm1_2Permissions
    Permissions that regulate access to TPM 1.2
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ChannelProviderPermission.Action
    Enumeration of actions for ChannelProvider permissions.
